<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Home4YOU - Turn your dream home into reality</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="With over 30 years of experience, our firm specializes in designing modern homes that blend innovation with comfort." />
		<meta name="author" content="lukaszwiniarczyk - github" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Marcellus&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@100;400;700&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet" />
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/style.min.css" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<header class="header">
			<nav class="nav">
				<a class="nav__logo" href="./">Home<span>4YOU</span></a>
				<button class="nav__btn" aria-label="Menu">
					<i class="ti ti-menu"></i>
				</button>
				<div class="nav__links">
					<a class="nav__links--link" href="./#offer">offer</a>
					<a class="nav__links--link" href="./#realizations">realizations</a>
					<a class="nav__links--link" href="./#career">career</a>
					<a class="nav__links--link" href="./#contact">contact</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
			<nav class="nav-desktop wrapper">
				<a href="./" class="nav-desktop__logo">Home<span>4YOU</span></a>
				<div class="nav-desktop__links">
					<a class="nav-desktop__links--link" href="./#offer">offer</a>
					<a class="nav-desktop__links--link" href="./#realizations"
						>realizations</a
					>
					<a class="nav-desktop__links--link" href="./#career">career</a>
					<a class="nav-desktop__links--link" href="./#contact">contact</a>
				</div>
			</nav>
			<div class="header__box wrapper">
				<h1 class="header__box--heading">
					turn your dream home into reality with us
				</h1>
				<a class="header__box--cta" href="./#contact"
					>Check Now <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i
				></a>
			</div>
		</header>
		<main class="main">
			<section class="about-us wrapper">
				<div class="about-us__left">
					<h2 class="about-us__left--heading">
						Where Visionary Architecture Meets Contemporary Family Life
					</h2>
					<div class="about-us__left--img"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="about-us__right">
					<div class="about-us__right--img">
						<img
							src="dist/img/homeAboutUs.jpg"
							alt="Black house and beautiful garden" />
						<img
							src="dist/img/homeSecondAboutUs.jpg"
							alt="Different black house and beautiful garden" />
					</div>
					<p class="about-us__right--info">
						With over 30 years of experience, our firm specializes in designing
						modern homes that blend innovation with comfort. Our portfolio spans
						four continents, showcasing a global vision rooted in quality,
						creativity, and timeless design.
					</p>
					<div class="about-us__right--achievements">
						<div class="about-us__right--achievements-box">
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-number">100+</p>
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-text">
								Projects Completed Annually
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="about-us__right--achievements-box">
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-number">30+</p>
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-text">
								Years of Experience
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="about-us__right--achievements-box">
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-number">50+</p>
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-text">
								Employees hired
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="about-us__right--achievements-box">
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-number">35+</p>
							<p class="about-us__right--achievements-box-text">
								Worldwide Honors
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section class="offer wrapper" id="offer">
				<h2 class="offer__heading">Design. Plan. Create. Live.</h2>
				<p class="offer__info">What We Offer</p>
				<div class="offer__box">
					<div class="offer__box--home">
						<p class="offer__box--home-text">Compact Home Plan</p>
					</div>
					<div class="offer__box--home offer__box--home-second">
						<p class="offer__box--home-text">Medium Home Plan</p>
					</div>
					<div class="offer__box--home offer__box--home-third">
						<p class="offer__box--home-text">Large Home Plan</p>
					</div>
					<div class="offer__box--home offer__box--home-fourth">
						<p class="offer__box--home-text">Luxury Home Plan</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="offer__addons">
					<button class="offer__addons--btn">
						Check <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i>
					</button>
					<p class="offer__addons--part">
						<span class="offer__addons--part-type">1</span>/2
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section class="realizations" id="realizations">
				<div class="realizations__left">
					<h2 class="realizations__left--heading">Our Completed Projects</h2>
					<p class="realizations__left--info">
						Our projects combine modern design with everyday functionality. From
						small homes to larger residences, each one reflects our commitment
						to quality and innovation. Explore the homes we've created around
						the world.
					</p>
					<p class="realizations__left--info">
						With over 30 years of experience, we turn ideas into functional,
						lasting spaces. Each design is tailored to our clients’ needs,
						balancing aesthetics with smart, comfortable solutions built to
						stand the test of time.
					</p>
					<a class="realizations__left--btn" href="./#contact"
						>Create Your World <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i
					></a>
				</div>
				<div class="realizations__right">
					<div class="realizations__right--two">
						<div class="realizations__right--two-img">
							<p>Warsaw, Poland</p>
						</div>
						<div
							class="realizations__right--two-img realizations__right--two-img-second">
							<p>San Diego, USA</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="realizations__right--one">
						<p>Cape Town, RSA</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section class="career" id="career">
				<div class="wrapper career__box">
					<div class="career__box--left">
						<h2 class="career__box--left-heading">Join Our Team</h2>
						<img src="dist/img/womenContact.jpg" alt="Women" />
					</div>
					<div class="career__box--right">
						<p class="career__box--right-info">
							We’re always looking for passionate minds to join our growing
							team. At our company, you’ll work on inspiring projects that shape
							the future of modern living. We value creativity, collaboration,
							and a drive for excellence. If you’re ready to grow your career in
							a dynamic, design-focused environment — we’d love to meet you.
						</p>
						<a class="career__box--right-link" href="./#contact"
							>Contact Us <i class="ti ti-arrow-right"></i
						></a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			<section class="contact" id="contact">
				<h2 class="contact__heading">Get in Touch</h2>
				<div class="contact__box wrapper">
					<div class="contact__box--left">
						<form>
							<div class="contact__box--left-content">
								<label for="name"></label>
								<input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Name" required />
							</div>
							<div class="contact__box--left-content">
								<label for="email"></label>
								<input
									type="email"
									id="email"
									placeholder="Email Address"
									required />
							</div>
							<div class="contact__box--left-content">
								<label for="msg"></label>
								<textarea
									name="msg"
									id="msg"
									placeholder="Message"
									required></textarea>
							</div>
							<button>Send</button>
						</form>
					</div>
					<div class="contact__box--right">
						<div class="contact__box--right-info">
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-heading">Phone Number</p>
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-text">000 000 000</p>
						</div>
						<div class="contact__box--right-info">
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-heading">Email Address</p>
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-text">example@example.pl</p>
						</div>
						<div class="contact__box--right-info">
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-heading">Address</p>
							<p class="contact__box--right-info-text">San Diego, California</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<footer class="footer">
			<a href="./">Home<span>4YOU</span></a>
		</footer>

		<script src="dist/js/script.min.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
